| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4930 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2c40f8ae-79eb-5b1a-9efc-584e67e5f091"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
